help.title: Karma
help.description: This command is for viewing your karma

extensions.title: Trading
extensions.description: This command gives some of the caster's karma to the target mentioned user. The correct use is ``!t karma trade @mention amount``

extensions.title: Check
extensions.description: This command shows the karma of mentioned user. The correct use is ``!t karma check @mention``

extensions.title: Leaderboad
extensions.description: Display a leaderboard of with the top five users. The correct use is ``!t karma leaderboard``

help.title: Data
help.description: Checks some statistics of the bot

extensions.title: Uptime
extensions.description: Show the uptime of the bot in days

help.title: Random
help.description: Use ``@Teslovian /random {Your Text}`` to generate ``{Your Text}`` on an Image

help.title: Shirt
help.description: Use ``@Teslovian /shirt {Your Text}`` to generate an T-Shirt with ``{Your Text}`` on it

help.title: Place
help.description: Use ``@Teslovian /place {Your Text}`` to replace the location in a random image ``{Your Text}``

help.title: I'm
help.description: Use ``@Teslovian /by {Your Text}`` to replace text with an aspect of you from ``{Your Text}``

help.title: By
help.description: Use ``@Teslovian /by {Your Text}`` to generate an Image with a text referring to ``{Your Text}``
